pageProduct.name: Sensuous Smooth Natural Water Based Lubricant 100ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

This premium personal lubricant has been uniquely formulated with natural ingredients including soothing Aloe Vera to stimulate and replenish the body's own natural lubrication. It is colourless and feels just like the real thing.

Smooth is an excellent alternative to chemical based lubricants. Smooth is dermatologically tested and  contains no glycerin or parabens which makes it one of the safest on the market giving you the confidence to enjoy love how it was meant to be.

Smooth is formulated with Aloe Vera which has natural lubrication qualities as well as soothing and healing characteristics.

Made in Australia
